sqlMap.statement:
SELECT TASK.SVC_TASK_NUM AS SVC_TASK_NUM FROM SVC_TASK TASK WHERE TASK.GLBL_CMPY_CD = #glblCmpyCd# AND TASK.EZCANCELFLAG = '0'
#taskPrintStsCd[]#
AND TASK.SVC_TASK_STS_CD <> #debriefErr#

SELECT T.GLBL_CMPY_CD AS GLBL_CMPY_CD ,FV.TECH_CD AS TECH_CD ,T.SVC_TASK_NUM AS SVC_TASK_NUM ,T.MDL_NM AS MDL_NM ,T.SER_NUM AS SER_NUM ,STC.DS_ACCT_NM AS DS_ACCT_NM ,DECODE(STC.FIRST_LINE_ADDR, NULL, '', STC.FIRST_LINE_ADDR || ' ') || DECODE(STC.SCD_LINE_ADDR, NULL, '', STC.SCD_LINE_ADDR || ' ') || DECODE(STC.THIRD_LINE_ADDR, NULL, '', STC.THIRD_LINE_ADDR || ' ') || DECODE(STC.FRTH_LINE_ADDR, NULL, '', STC.FRTH_LINE_ADDR) AS SHIP_TO_LINE_ADDR ,STC.CTY_ADDR AS SHIP_TO_CTY_ADDR ,STC.ST_CD AS SHIP_TO_ST_CD ,T.SVC_CUST_ATTN_TXT AS SVC_CUST_CLLR_TXT ,STC.LOC_NM AS SHIP_TO_LOC_NM ,T.CUST_TEL_NUM AS CUST_TEL_NUM ,STC.POST_CD AS SHIP_TO_POST_CD ,T.DS_SVC_CALL_TP_CD AS DS_SVC_CALL_TP_CD ,DSCT.DS_SVC_CALL_TP_DESC_TXT AS DS_SVC_CALL_TP_DESC_TXT ,T.SVC_BILL_TP_CD AS SVC_BILL_TP_CD ,SBT.SVC_BILL_TP_DESC_TXT AS SVC_BILL_TP_DESC_TXT ,FVT.SVC_PBLM_TP_CD AS SVC_PBLM_TP_CD ,SPT.SVC_PBLM_TP_DESC_TXT AS SVC_PBLM_TP_DESC_TXT ,F.SVC_PBLM_TP_CD AS OPEN_SVC_PBLM_TP_CD ,OSPT.SVC_PBLM_TP_DESC_TXT AS OPEN_SVC_PBLM_TP_DESC_TXT ,FVT.SVC_PBLM_LOC_TP_CD AS SVC_PBLM_LOC_TP_CD ,SPLT.SVC_PBLM_LOC_TP_DESC_TXT AS SVC_PBLM_LOC_TP_DESC_TXT ,FVT.SVC_PBLM_RSN_TP_CD AS SVC_PBLM_RSN_TP_CD ,SPRT.SVC_PBLM_RSN_TP_DESC_TXT AS SVC_PBLM_RSN_TP_DESC_TXT ,FVT.SVC_PBLM_CRCT_TP_CD AS SVC_PBLM_CRCT_TP_CD ,SPCT.SVC_PBLM_CRCT_TP_DESC_TXT AS SVC_PBLM_CRCT_TP_DESC_TXT ,DECODE(FV.FSR_VISIT_ARV_DT, NULL, NULL, DECODE(FV.FSR_VISIT_ARV_TM, NULL, NULL, FV.FSR_VISIT_ARV_DT || FV.FSR_VISIT_ARV_TM || '000')) AS CALL_START_DT_TM_TXT ,DECODE(FV.FSR_VISIT_CPLT_DT, NULL, NULL, DECODE(FV.FSR_VISIT_CPLT_TM, NULL, NULL, FV.FSR_VISIT_CPLT_DT || FV.FSR_VISIT_CPLT_TM || '000')) AS CALL_CPLT_DT_TM_TXT ,FVT.SVC_LBOR_TM_NUM AS LBOR_TM_AMT
,NVL(FVT.SVC_LBOR_FUNC_AMT, 0) - NVL(FVT.SVC_LBOR_FUNC_DISC_AMT, 0) AS SVC_LBOR_TOT_AMT
,FVT.SVC_LBOR_UNIT_HRS_AOT AS SVC_MIN_CHRG_HRS_AMT ,SM.SVC_CMNT_TXT AS SVC_CMNT_TXT ,T.SIGNA_FILE_PATH_TXT AS SIGNA_FILE_PATH_TXT
,T.SEND_RPT_EML_ADDR AS CUST_EML_ADDR
,T.INV_CCY_CD AS INV_CCY_CD FROM SVC_TASK T ,FSR F ,FSR_VISIT FV ,FSR_VISIT_TASK FVT ,SHIP_TO_CUST STC ,DS_SVC_CALL_TP DSCT ,SVC_BILL_TP SBT ,SVC_PBLM_TP SPT ,SVC_PBLM_TP OSPT ,SVC_PBLM_LOC_TP SPLT ,SVC_PBLM_RSN_TP SPRT ,SVC_PBLM_CRCT_TP SPCT ,( SELECT * FROM ( SELECT MEMO.GLBL_CMPY_CD ,MEMO.EZCANCELFLAG ,MEMO.FSR_NUM ,MEMO.SVC_TASK_NUM ,MEMO.SVC_CMNT_TXT FROM SVC_TASK TASK ,SVC_MEMO MEMO WHERE TASK.GLBL_CMPY_CD = #glblCmpyCd# AND TASK.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' AND TASK.SVC_TASK_NUM = #svcTaskNum# AND TASK.GLBL_CMPY_CD = MEMO.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND TASK.EZCANCELFLAG = MEMO.EZCANCELFLAG AND TASK.FSR_NUM = MEMO.FSR_NUM AND TASK.SVC_TASK_NUM = MEMO.SVC_TASK_NUM AND MEMO.SVC_MEMO_CATG_CD = #svcMemoCatgCd#
#svcMemoTpCd[]#
ORDER BY MEMO.LAST_UPD_TS DESC ) A WHERE ROWNUM = 1 ) SM WHERE T.GLBL_CMPY_CD = #glblCmpyCd# AND T.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' AND T.SVC_TASK_NUM = #svcTaskNum# AND T.GLBL_CMPY_CD = F.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND T.EZCANCELFLAG = F.EZCANCELFLAG AND T.FSR_NUM = F.FSR_NUM AND T.GLBL_CMPY_CD = FV.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND T.EZCANCELFLAG = FV.EZCANCELFLAG AND T.FSR_NUM = FV.FSR_NUM AND T.SVC_TASK_NUM = FV.SVC_TASK_NUM AND FV.GLBL_CMPY_CD = FVT.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND FV.EZCANCELFLAG = FVT.EZCANCELFLAG AND FV.FSR_NUM = FVT.FSR_NUM AND FV.SVC_TASK_NUM = FVT.SVC_TASK_NUM AND FV.FSR_VISIT_NUM = FVT.FSR_VISIT_NUM AND F.GLBL_CMPY_CD = STC.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND F.EZCANCELFLAG = STC.EZCANCELFLAG AND NVL(F.SHIP_TO_UPD_CUST_CD, F.SHIP_TO_CUST_CD) = STC.SHIP_TO_CUST_CD AND T.GLBL_CMPY_CD = DSCT.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND T.EZCANCELFLAG = DSCT.EZCANCELFLAG AND T.DS_SVC_CALL_TP_CD = DSCT.DS_SVC_CALL_TP_CD AND T.GLBL_CMPY_CD = SBT.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND T.EZCANCELFLAG = SBT.EZCANCELFLAG AND T.SVC_BILL_TP_CD = SBT.SVC_BILL_TP_CD
AND FVT.GLBL_CMPY_CD = SPT.GLBL_CMPY_CD (+) AND FVT.EZCANCELFLAG = SPT.EZCANCELFLAG (+) AND FVT.SVC_PBLM_TP_CD = SPT.SVC_PBLM_TP_CD (+) AND F.GLBL_CMPY_CD = OSPT.GLBL_CMPY_CD (+) AND F.EZCANCELFLAG = OSPT.EZCANCELFLAG (+) AND F.SVC_PBLM_TP_CD = OSPT.SVC_PBLM_TP_CD (+) AND FVT.GLBL_CMPY_CD = SPLT.GLBL_CMPY_CD (+) AND FVT.EZCANCELFLAG = SPLT.EZCANCELFLAG (+) AND FVT.SVC_PBLM_LOC_TP_CD = SPLT.SVC_PBLM_LOC_TP_CD (+) AND FVT.GLBL_CMPY_CD = SPRT.GLBL_CMPY_CD (+) AND FVT.EZCANCELFLAG = SPRT.EZCANCELFLAG (+) AND FVT.SVC_PBLM_RSN_TP_CD = SPRT.SVC_PBLM_RSN_TP_CD (+) AND FVT.GLBL_CMPY_CD = SPCT.GLBL_CMPY_CD (+) AND FVT.EZCANCELFLAG = SPCT.EZCANCELFLAG (+) AND FVT.SVC_PBLM_CRCT_TP_CD = SPCT.SVC_PBLM_CRCT_TP_CD (+)
AND T.GLBL_CMPY_CD = SM.GLBL_CMPY_CD (+) AND T.EZCANCELFLAG = SM.EZCANCELFLAG (+) AND T.FSR_NUM = SM.FSR_NUM (+) AND T.SVC_TASK_NUM = SM.SVC_TASK_NUM (+)

SELECT READ.GLBL_CMPY_CD AS GLBL_CMPY_CD ,READ.EZCANCELFLAG AS EZCANCELFLAG ,READ.FSR_NUM AS FSR_NUM ,READ.SVC_TASK_NUM AS SVC_TASK_NUM ,READ.FSR_VISIT_NUM AS FSR_VISIT_NUM ,READ.MTR_LB_CD AS MTR_LB_CD ,ML.MTR_LB_NM AS MTR_LB_DESC_TXT ,READ.READ_MTR_CNT AS READ_MTR_CNT ,READ.TEST_MTR_CNT AS TEST_MTR_CNT ,ROWNUM AS MTR_SORT_NUM FROM SVC_TASK TASK ,FSR_VISIT VIS ,SVC_PHYS_MTR_READ READ ,MTR_LB ML WHERE TASK.GLBL_CMPY_CD = #glblCmpyCd# AND TASK.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' AND TASK.SVC_TASK_NUM = #svcTaskNum# AND TASK.GLBL_CMPY_CD = VIS.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND TASK.EZCANCELFLAG = VIS.EZCANCELFLAG AND TASK.FSR_NUM = VIS.FSR_NUM AND TASK.SVC_TASK_NUM = VIS.SVC_TASK_NUM AND VIS.GLBL_CMPY_CD = READ.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND VIS.EZCANCELFLAG = READ.EZCANCELFLAG AND VIS.FSR_NUM = READ.FSR_NUM AND VIS.SVC_TASK_NUM = READ.SVC_TASK_NUM AND VIS.FSR_VISIT_NUM = READ.FSR_VISIT_NUM AND READ.DS_TEST_COPY_CLS_CD = #dsTestCopyClsCd# AND READ.GLBL_CMPY_CD = ML.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND READ.EZCANCELFLAG = ML.EZCANCELFLAG AND READ.MTR_LB_CD = ML.MTR_LB_CD
AND READ.VLD_MTR_FLG = 'Y'
AND ( EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM SVC_MACH_MSTR A ,DS_MDL_MTR B WHERE READ.GLBL_CMPY_CD = A.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND READ.SVC_MACH_MSTR_PK = A.SVC_MACH_MSTR_PK AND A.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' AND A.GLBL_CMPY_CD = B.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND A.MTR_GRP_PK = B.MTR_GRP_PK AND READ.MTR_LB_CD = B.MDL_MTR_LB_CD AND B.TECH_READ_MND_FLG = #techReadMndFlg# AND B.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' ) OR EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM CONTR_PHYS_BLLG_MTR_RELN A ,DS_CONTR_BLLG_MTR B ,DS_CONTR_DTL C ,DS_CONTR_DTL_STS_V D WHERE READ.GLBL_CMPY_CD = A.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND READ.SVC_MACH_MSTR_PK = A.MACH_MSTR_PK AND READ.SVC_PHYS_MTR_PK = A.SVC_PHYS_MTR_PK AND A.BLLBL_FLG = 'Y' AND A.ACTV_FLG = 'Y' AND A.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' AND A.GLBL_CMPY_CD = B.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND A.DS_CONTR_BLLG_MTR_PK = B.DS_CONTR_BLLG_MTR_PK AND B.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' AND B.GLBL_CMPY_CD = C.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND B.DS_CONTR_DTL_PK = C.DS_CONTR_DTL_PK AND C.CONTR_EFF_FROM_DT <= #slsDt# AND NVL(C.CONTR_CLO_DT, C.CONTR_EFF_THRU_DT) >= #slsDt# AND C.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' AND C.GLBL_CMPY_CD = D.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND C.DS_CONTR_DTL_PK = D.DS_CONTR_DTL_PK AND D.ETTL_AVAL_FLG = 'Y' AND D.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' ) )
ORDER BY READ.FSR_NUM ,READ.SVC_TASK_NUM ,READ.FSR_VISIT_NUM ,ML.MTR_LB_SORT_NUM

SELECT USG.GLBL_CMPY_CD AS GLBL_CMPY_CD ,USG.EZCANCELFLAG AS EZCANCELFLAG ,USG.FSR_NUM AS FSR_NUM ,USG.SVC_TASK_NUM AS SVC_TASK_NUM ,USG.FSR_VISIT_NUM AS FSR_VISIT_NUM ,USG.MDSE_CD AS MDSE_CD ,M.MDSE_DESC_SHORT_TXT AS MDSE_DESC_SHORT_TXT ,USG.SVC_PRT_QTY AS SVC_PRT_QTY ,USG.SVC_PRT_FUNC_AMT - USG.SVC_PRT_FUNC_DISC_AMT AS PRT_TOT_PRC_AMT ,ROWNUM AS PRT_SORT_NUM FROM SVC_TASK TASK ,FSR_VISIT VIS ,FSR_USG USG ,MDSE M WHERE TASK.GLBL_CMPY_CD = #glblCmpyCd# AND TASK.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' AND TASK.SVC_TASK_NUM = #svcTaskNum# AND TASK.GLBL_CMPY_CD = VIS.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND TASK.EZCANCELFLAG = VIS.EZCANCELFLAG AND TASK.FSR_NUM = VIS.FSR_NUM AND TASK.SVC_TASK_NUM = VIS.SVC_TASK_NUM AND VIS.GLBL_CMPY_CD = USG.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND VIS.EZCANCELFLAG = USG.EZCANCELFLAG AND VIS.FSR_NUM = USG.FSR_NUM AND VIS.SVC_TASK_NUM = USG.SVC_TASK_NUM AND VIS.FSR_VISIT_NUM = USG.FSR_VISIT_NUM AND USG.GLBL_CMPY_CD = M.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND USG.EZCANCELFLAG = M.EZCANCELFLAG AND USG.MDSE_CD = M.MDSE_CD ORDER BY USG.FSR_NUM ,USG.SVC_TASK_NUM ,USG.FSR_VISIT_NUM ,USG.MDSE_CD

SELECT SMDI.MDSE_CD AS MDSE_CD ,M.MDSE_DESC_SHORT_TXT AS MDSE_DESC_SHORT_TXT ,SMDI.SVC_MOD_QTY AS SVC_MOD_QTY ,ROWNUM AS MOD_PRT_SORT_NUM FROM SVC_MOD_STS SMS ,SVC_MOD_DTL_ITEM SMDI ,MDSE M WHERE SMS.GLBL_CMPY_CD = #glblCmpyCd# AND SMS.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' AND SMS.SVC_TASK_NUM = #svcTaskNum# AND SMS.GLBL_CMPY_CD = SMDI.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND SMS.EZCANCELFLAG = SMDI.EZCANCELFLAG AND SMS.SVC_MOD_DTL_PK = SMDI.SVC_MOD_DTL_PK AND SMDI.GLBL_CMPY_CD = M.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND SMDI.EZCANCELFLAG = M.EZCANCELFLAG AND SMDI.MDSE_CD = M.MDSE_CD ORDER BY SMS.SVC_TASK_NUM ,SMDI.MDSE_CD

SELECT SHIP.CTRY_CD ,SHIP.POST_CD FROM SVC_TASK TASK ,FSR ,SHIP_TO_CUST SHIP WHERE TASK.GLBL_CMPY_CD = #glblCmpyCd# AND TASK.SVC_TASK_NUM = #svcTaskNum# AND TASK.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' AND TASK.GLBL_CMPY_CD = FSR.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND TASK.FSR_NUM = FSR.FSR_NUM AND FSR.EZCANCELFLAG = '0' AND ( CASE WHEN FSR.SHIP_TO_CUST_UPD_FLG = 'Y' THEN FSR.SHIP_TO_UPD_CUST_CD ELSE FSR.SHIP_TO_CUST_CD END ) = SHIP.SHIP_TO_CUST_CD AND FSR.GLBL_CMPY_CD = SHIP.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND SHIP.EZCANCELFLAG = '0'

SELECT A.FSR_CPLT_LTR_WRK_PK ,A.SVC_TASK_NUM ,A.CUST_EML_ADDR ,A.SVC_CUST_CLLR_TXT
,A.DS_ACCT_NM ,A.SER_NUM ,A.TECH_CD
FROM FSR_CPLT_LTR_WRK A
,SVC_TASK B
WHERE A.GLBL_CMPY_CD = #glblCmpyCd# AND A.EZCANCELFLAG = '0'
AND A.GLBL_CMPY_CD = B.GLBL_CMPY_CD AND A.SVC_TASK_NUM = B.SVC_TASK_NUM AND B.EZCANCELFLAG = '0'
#taskPrintStsCd[]#
